<span class="usa-tag pmc-tag-pt">editorial</span> <div class="display-inline-block"><button type="button" class="cursor-pointer text-no-underline bg-transparent border-0 padding-0 text-left margin-0 text-normal text-primary" aria-controls="journal_context_menu">J Biomed Inform</button></div>. 2020 Apr 23;105:103433. doi: <a href="https://doi.org/10.1016/j.jbi.2020.103433" class="usa-link usa-link--external" data-ga-action="click_feat_suppl" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">10.1016/j.jbi.2020.103433</a>
